    "Moreover, the UI to interact with LLMs is not provided by oTree itself.",
    "particular use cases, such as the one developed by Chopra et al. (2023), which is designed specifically for LLM applications in interview settings.",
    "Another challenge lies in the lack of interface standardization.",
